<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #ecfeff, #f0fdf4); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #0f766e; margin: 0;">ğŸ New wishlist items for <%= @event.name %></h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hi <%= @participant.name %>,</p>

  <p><strong><%= @giftee.name %></strong> just added items to their wishlist.</p>

  <div style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #374151;">View their wishlist</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0;">See the latest ideas and pick something they'll love.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="<%= @magic_link %>" style="background: #0ea5e9; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
      Open wishlist
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
    We'll keep you posted if they add more items later.
  </p>

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">

  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
    Secret Santa by <%= link_to "secretsanta.gronare.com", root_url, style: "color: #3b82f6;" %>
  </p>
</body>
</html>
